1
00:00:10,208 --> 00:00:12,250
[water flowing]

2
00:00:12,333 --> 00:00:14,541
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

3
00:00:14,625 --> 00:00:17,666
SHEN-LUNG WATER

4
00:00:17,750 --> 00:00:19,958
IMMEASURABLE LIFE

5
00:00:20,041 --> 00:00:22,583
LIFE

6
00:00:22,666 --> 00:00:23,833
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

7
00:00:23,916 --> 00:00:25,375
[suspenseful music playing]

8
00:00:25,458 --> 00:00:27,666
- [man shouts]
- [woman whimpers]

9
00:00:27,750 --> 00:00:29,166
- Is that him?
- Yes.

10
00:00:30,208 --> 00:00:31,833
[gangster] Where do you think
you're going?

11
00:00:31,916 --> 00:00:33,375
You scam me. Then you fuck my wife!

12
00:00:34,083 --> 00:00:36,791
- [man] Religious scammer.
- [gangster] Let's get outta here.

13
00:00:38,166 --> 00:00:40,625
[suspenseful music continues]

14
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:45,500
[labored breathing]

15
00:00:49,875 --> 00:00:53,083
[Chi-sha] Shen-Lung Crown Prince,
you're dying.

16
00:00:54,083 --> 00:00:57,958
I can save you.
But you must pay the price.

17
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,750
Just take my hand,

18
00:01:01,708 --> 00:01:04,166
and you can change your fate.

19
00:01:04,250 --> 00:01:06,250
[breathing nervously]

20
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,875
[suspenseful music continues]

21
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:18,333
[screaming]

22
00:01:28,333 --> 00:01:31,125
AGENT FROM ABOVE

23
00:01:32,958 --> 00:01:36,458
SOUL HARVEST

24
00:01:36,958 --> 00:01:38,958
DONGFENG MARKET

25
00:01:49,083 --> 00:01:51,250
[dramatic music playing]

26
00:01:58,666 --> 00:02:00,916
- Everyone, time to eat!
- [all cheer]

27
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:04,791
- [funky music playing]
- [male ghost] Thank you so much.

28
00:02:04,875 --> 00:02:08,208
- What a feast! Oh, so good.
- [slurps] Oh my God.

29
00:02:08,291 --> 00:02:10,250
That's delicious! [chuckles]

30
00:02:10,333 --> 00:02:11,750
Eat to your heart's content.

31
00:02:12,333 --> 00:02:13,625
Welcome, everyone.

32
00:02:13,708 --> 00:02:17,083
Please enjoy, and let me know
if you'd like me to make you anything.

33
00:02:17,166 --> 00:02:19,833
Oh, help yourself.
There's enough for everyone.

34
00:02:20,416 --> 00:02:23,041
- Please, help yourself. Try some of these.
- C cup?

35
00:02:23,125 --> 00:02:24,458
- [comical music plays]
- Eat slowly.

36
00:02:24,541 --> 00:02:26,000
[male ghost] This is so good!

37
00:02:26,083 --> 00:02:30,500
- Uh, hi, I'm Mei-na. Nice to meet you.
- Hello, I'm Wang Hsiao-ming.

38
00:02:31,541 --> 00:02:34,041
- Would you marry a ghost ever?
- [music stops]

39
00:02:45,791 --> 00:02:46,833
[Han Chieh] Hsiao-ming.

40
00:02:50,708 --> 00:02:51,708
What's up?

41
00:02:52,291 --> 00:02:53,416
Take your pick.

42
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:58,708
- [giggling] All this for me?
- [comical music playing]

43
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:01,375
That's so nice of you.

44
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,833
So ugly. Wear a suit like a gentleman.

45
00:03:05,625 --> 00:03:08,166
Well, he just looks like a nerd. Ha!

46
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:11,666
You should be
more encouraging to Hsiao Ming.

47
00:03:12,166 --> 00:03:13,666
Come on, let's try them on.

48
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:15,000
Together? [laughs]

49
00:03:15,083 --> 00:03:16,958
- Together?
- What do you mean together?

50
00:03:17,041 --> 00:03:19,875
- Not gentlemanly.
- [Hsiao-ming] Why don't you come with us?

51
00:03:21,041 --> 00:03:24,791
Han, did you meet Miss Cheng yet?
She moved in recently.

52
00:03:24,875 --> 00:03:26,791
[chatter in the background]

53
00:03:26,875 --> 00:03:29,416
I saw her daughter. I think she's deaf.

54
00:03:30,416 --> 00:03:31,583
[sighs]

55
00:03:31,666 --> 00:03:34,750
She's had quite a hard life, it seems.

56
00:03:34,833 --> 00:03:38,208
It's okay. Invite her
to my restaurant when you're free.

57
00:03:38,291 --> 00:03:39,125
Han.

58
00:03:40,041 --> 00:03:42,416
You should say hello to her. Huh?

59
00:03:45,375 --> 00:03:47,291
[curious music playing]

60
00:03:48,208 --> 00:03:49,041
Ta-da!

61
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:51,458
- [music intensifies]
- [all applaud]

62
00:03:51,541 --> 00:03:54,791
[grandma 1] Oh!

63
00:03:54,875 --> 00:03:57,500
- [grandma 2] Oh gosh, dear. It's ancient.
- So old-fashioned.

64
00:03:57,583 --> 00:04:00,791
You look like an old man. Old man Wang!

65
00:04:00,875 --> 00:04:01,833
[grandmas laugh]

66
00:04:02,625 --> 00:04:05,750
[male ghost] You look dashing,
young man! Very classy.

67
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:07,166
[laughter]

68
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:08,791
They're all getting along.

69
00:04:09,916 --> 00:04:12,000
[grandmas laugh]

70
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,833
Ms. Lo's good for the old man.

71
00:04:16,333 --> 00:04:18,583
[poignant music playing]

72
00:04:18,666 --> 00:04:21,250
[Yeh Tzu] Did their families die
in that fire too?

73
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:22,333
[Han Chieh] Mmm.

74
00:04:23,541 --> 00:04:26,958
Ms. Lo's younger brother
and the old man's son and grandson,

75
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,958
they all want their families around them.

76
00:04:30,833 --> 00:04:32,250
That's why I'm helping.

77
00:04:34,833 --> 00:04:38,708
I never knew why
Ms. Lo's younger brother never reconciled.

78
00:04:39,541 --> 00:04:42,041
- [all laugh]
- I hope soon she can move on.

79
00:04:43,375 --> 00:04:44,750
[poignant music continues]

80
00:04:46,083 --> 00:04:50,166
You know, even though you frown a lot,
underneath, you're really a good guy.

81
00:04:54,958 --> 00:04:58,625
You're never at home, always here.
You take medicines?

82
00:04:59,541 --> 00:05:00,791
Of course.

83
00:05:03,583 --> 00:05:05,250
Hey. Smile!

84
00:05:05,833 --> 00:05:06,833
[camera clicks]

85
00:05:08,083 --> 00:05:09,083
What?

86
00:05:17,208 --> 00:05:18,250
[phone chimes]

87
00:05:22,083 --> 00:05:23,166
MESSAGE FROM CHANG MIN

88
00:05:23,250 --> 00:05:25,708
<i>Gangsters from Heilung Hall</i>
<i>were massacred last night.</i>

89
00:05:25,791 --> 00:05:28,750
<i>The way they were killed was very strange.</i>
<i>I need your help.</i>

90
00:05:28,833 --> 00:05:30,666
[tense music playing]

91
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:33,875
SAFETY FOR THE WHOLE FAMILY

92
00:05:33,958 --> 00:05:35,958
[coughing]

93
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:42,750
She's had quite a hard life, it seems.

94
00:05:42,833 --> 00:05:45,166
You should say hello to her.  Huh?

95
00:05:49,083 --> 00:05:50,166
I'm Han.

96
00:05:50,958 --> 00:05:52,208
I live next door.

97
00:05:53,875 --> 00:05:57,500
You're the agent from above
Ms. Lo mentioned, right?

98
00:05:59,541 --> 00:06:00,583
[exhales]

99
00:06:00,666 --> 00:06:06,416
Everyone's at a gathering on the rooftop.
Ms. Lo hoped you'd bring your daughter.

100
00:06:06,916 --> 00:06:12,083
Oh. Yuan-yuan is deaf and mute.
I don't want to trouble everyone.

101
00:06:12,166 --> 00:06:14,291
- Yes, I saw her.
- [somber music playing]

102
00:06:14,375 --> 00:06:15,750
She's very lively.

103
00:06:15,833 --> 00:06:17,416
She likes drawing.

104
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,500
- [eerie music playing]
- [heavy breathing]

105
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,000
[door opens]

106
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,125
[melancholy music playing]

107
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:42,750
[Han Chieh] I'll leave you be.

108
00:06:42,833 --> 00:06:44,458
Um… Master Han.

109
00:06:44,541 --> 00:06:48,375
I've been very sick for years,
and my daughter needs your help.

110
00:06:48,458 --> 00:06:49,958
I don't do that.

111
00:06:51,625 --> 00:06:53,125
I'm just an ordinary person.

112
00:06:53,958 --> 00:06:56,000
- [sighs]
- I'm sorry.

113
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,875
[door opens]

114
00:07:00,833 --> 00:07:02,208
[door closes]

115
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,000
[melancholy music continues]

116
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,833
LINGERING SPIRIT

117
00:07:10,916 --> 00:07:11,916
[camera clicking]

118
00:07:14,625 --> 00:07:17,625
SHEN-LUNG CROWN PRINCE
BEWITCHED BY OCCULTIST TO COMMIT CRIME

119
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:40,416
[music fades]

120
00:07:52,083 --> 00:07:54,708
TEMPLE FIRE, TWO DEATHS

121
00:07:54,791 --> 00:07:56,125
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

122
00:07:58,125 --> 00:08:00,458
[dramatic music playing]

123
00:08:00,541 --> 00:08:02,333
TEMPLE HOLDOUT RESIDENTS GET MURDERED

124
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:05,833
LIU KUAN-FU REFUTES:
"IT HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH ME"

125
00:08:06,416 --> 00:08:08,666
ARSON LINKED TO LAND DISPUTE?

126
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,791
LIU KUAN-FU RETORTS:
"WHERE'S THE PROOF?"

127
00:08:14,208 --> 00:08:18,166
"WHERE'S THE PROOF?"

128
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,458
[phone buzzing]

129
00:08:26,041 --> 00:08:27,791
CHANG MIN CALLING

130
00:08:31,916 --> 00:08:34,708
[knocking on the door]

131
00:08:37,333 --> 00:08:38,875
I was calling you.

132
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:42,000
You never have good news.

133
00:08:42,083 --> 00:08:43,375
- [door closes]
- Hey.

134
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:46,208
Look. Hmm.

135
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,291
- [dramatic music playing]
- [Han Chieh] Vasavatti?

136
00:08:51,625 --> 00:08:54,541
Heilung Hall.
Eleven people died, all very strange.

137
00:08:59,083 --> 00:09:00,875
[Han Chieh] That's Chi-sha.

138
00:09:00,958 --> 00:09:03,333
We can't rule out
that this was a paid hit.

139
00:09:03,416 --> 00:09:05,000
They had many enemies.

140
00:09:05,083 --> 00:09:06,666
He doesn't kill for money.

141
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:09,333
This is the work of Vasavatti.

142
00:09:10,833 --> 00:09:12,708
This is no gangster fight.

143
00:09:12,791 --> 00:09:14,375
[dramatic music continues]

144
00:09:18,833 --> 00:09:20,333
WUMENG OCCULTIST COLLUDES WITH GANGSTERS

145
00:09:20,416 --> 00:09:24,333
[the Crown Prince] It's what I expect from
my agent from above. Naturally rebellious.

146
00:09:24,416 --> 00:09:26,291
[dramatic music continues]

147
00:09:26,375 --> 00:09:28,208
There's a gangster at the temple.

148
00:09:28,291 --> 00:09:30,916
<i>I'll ask him. Maybe he'll know something.</i>

149
00:09:32,375 --> 00:09:33,625
Her… Here through here.

150
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:34,916
- A-Fu.
- Have a seat.

151
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,166
You must be rich now.

152
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,833
- Huh?
- This big temple.

153
00:09:38,333 --> 00:09:40,583
Have you returned to your old ways?

154
00:09:40,666 --> 00:09:43,750
Oh, no. No way.
I'm not like that. Hey, Han.

155
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:44,791
[chuckling] Hey.

156
00:09:44,875 --> 00:09:47,916
I don't scam people
with fake lottery numbers anymore.

157
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:51,416
At this temple,
after the management fees,

158
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:54,416
I donate everything
we make from offerings to charity.

159
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:57,333
- [intriguing music playing]
- I feed the homeless.

160
00:09:57,416 --> 00:09:58,708
And do beach cleanups.

161
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,833
[tuts] Look, I'll show you the accounts--

162
00:10:02,916 --> 00:10:04,250
- Forget it.
- [music stops]

163
00:10:04,333 --> 00:10:05,875
I'm not here for that.

164
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,791
Have you looked into what I asked of you?

165
00:10:18,125 --> 00:10:20,875
Well, I have heard back from a friend,

166
00:10:20,958 --> 00:10:22,958
that Heilung Hall has won

167
00:10:23,041 --> 00:10:26,375
a government construction project
worth over 100 million.

168
00:10:26,458 --> 00:10:30,000
Apparently Kuan-fu
and Heilung Hall had a deal.

169
00:10:30,083 --> 00:10:33,708
Heilung Hall subcontracted the work
to Kuan-fu.

170
00:10:34,375 --> 00:10:36,833
Later on, I don't know
if they had a fight,

171
00:10:36,916 --> 00:10:39,291
but Heilung Hall took all the money.

172
00:10:40,041 --> 00:10:41,208
[tense music playing]

173
00:10:41,291 --> 00:10:42,708
[exhales deeply]

174
00:10:42,791 --> 00:10:46,500
[tuts] Yeah, well, we've always known
those two didn't get along,

175
00:10:46,583 --> 00:10:49,250
and we thought something bad might happen.

176
00:10:49,333 --> 00:10:53,500
I just didn't expect
that Kuan-fu would be so ruthless.

177
00:10:53,583 --> 00:10:55,833
- Huh?
- [tense music continues]

178
00:10:55,916 --> 00:10:57,541
Of course he is.

179
00:10:58,541 --> 00:11:01,333
He set fire to
our family temple back then.

180
00:11:01,875 --> 00:11:04,041
<i>He wanted my family's land.</i>

181
00:11:04,125 --> 00:11:06,333
<i>His people forced me into drug addiction,</i>

182
00:11:07,125 --> 00:11:08,916
<i>so I'd owe him a big debt.</i>

183
00:11:09,416 --> 00:11:10,750
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

184
00:11:10,833 --> 00:11:14,125
<i>He said if I put up the title</i>
<i>to the temple as collateral,</i>

185
00:11:14,208 --> 00:11:16,041
<i>I could pay him back slowly.</i>

186
00:11:16,125 --> 00:11:18,625
[dramatic music playing]

187
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:30,333
LAND OWNERSHIP CERTIFICATE

188
00:11:32,291 --> 00:11:33,541
[man] Kneel!

189
00:11:33,625 --> 00:11:35,916
Try explaining this to the Crown Prince.

190
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:39,208
The construction company claims
that the temple's land is theirs.

191
00:11:39,291 --> 00:11:41,625
- [mom] Enough!
- What have you done, you unfilial son?

192
00:11:41,708 --> 00:11:43,083
[mom] Please. Please! Stop!

193
00:11:43,166 --> 00:11:45,291
[dad] What did we ever do
to deserve a son like you?

194
00:11:46,291 --> 00:11:48,250
[breathes heavily]

195
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:53,541
<i>My father would not give in.</i>

196
00:11:53,625 --> 00:11:56,291
<i>But Kuan-Fu burned the temple</i>
<i>to the ground.</i>

197
00:11:56,791 --> 00:11:58,750
[neighbor 1] How did this happen?

198
00:11:58,833 --> 00:12:01,541
- Is anyone still in there?
- [neighbor 2] All my stuff is gone.

199
00:12:01,625 --> 00:12:04,708
[neighbor 1] It's an inferno in there.
How did it start so quick?

200
00:12:04,791 --> 00:12:07,125
Where did it come from? Hey. Hey!

201
00:12:07,208 --> 00:12:09,375
- [neighbor 2] Hey, calm down.
- Wait. Don't go!

202
00:12:09,458 --> 00:12:11,458
[dramatic music continues]

203
00:12:29,333 --> 00:12:32,625
[Han Chieh] <i>In the end,</i>
<i>my mother and father died in that fire.</i>

204
00:12:32,708 --> 00:12:35,708
[crying]

205
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:49,500
<i>To this day, they're in hell,</i>
<i>suffering because of what I did.</i>

206
00:12:49,583 --> 00:12:51,583
[music turns more somber]

207
00:12:53,541 --> 00:12:55,666
I kill evil spirits.

208
00:12:56,708 --> 00:12:58,875
If that person is truly evil,

209
00:12:59,375 --> 00:13:02,583
then I'm not committing
a violation, am I?

210
00:13:03,666 --> 00:13:04,708
[music fades]

211
00:13:05,416 --> 00:13:06,416
[slurps]

212
00:13:07,666 --> 00:13:09,875
I get how you must feel.

213
00:13:10,375 --> 00:13:12,541
The Crown Prince knows
what happened to you,

214
00:13:12,625 --> 00:13:14,750
so he wants to give you a second chance.

215
00:13:14,833 --> 00:13:16,208
Hey, you better not waste it.

216
00:13:17,875 --> 00:13:18,791
You assume a lot.

217
00:13:18,875 --> 00:13:19,708
Hmm?

218
00:13:20,208 --> 00:13:21,708
You don't get it? Hey.

219
00:13:22,583 --> 00:13:24,041
It's like in Marvel.

220
00:13:24,125 --> 00:13:27,500
Imagine Iron Man just killing anyone.

221
00:13:27,583 --> 00:13:30,875
Iron Man became a hero
after changing his ways.

222
00:13:30,958 --> 00:13:33,625
You're also a superhero.

223
00:13:33,708 --> 00:13:36,416
Hey! With great power
comes great responsibility.

224
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:40,041
If you just kill anyone,
then you're no different from Kuan-fu.

225
00:13:42,125 --> 00:13:43,750
If I'm a superhero,

226
00:13:44,250 --> 00:13:45,583
what does that make you?

227
00:13:45,666 --> 00:13:46,625
Well…

228
00:13:48,041 --> 00:13:49,291
[funky music playing]

229
00:13:49,375 --> 00:13:50,291
I'm him.

230
00:13:56,041 --> 00:13:57,125
Truck driver?

231
00:13:57,208 --> 00:13:59,000
[horn honks]

232
00:13:59,083 --> 00:14:01,791
Not a truck driver. I'm Doctor Strange.

233
00:14:01,875 --> 00:14:04,916
Get it now? Doctor Strange.

234
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,083
Get it? You get it?

235
00:14:07,416 --> 00:14:10,375
I mean, I look just like him.
Hey, wait for me.

236
00:14:10,875 --> 00:14:11,875
[music ends]

237
00:14:18,666 --> 00:14:19,500
[man] Boss.

238
00:14:21,166 --> 00:14:22,166
[door closes]

239
00:14:25,541 --> 00:14:29,541
Boss, why did Chi-sha ask us
to come out here,

240
00:14:29,625 --> 00:14:31,041
in the middle of nowhere?

241
00:14:31,791 --> 00:14:33,291
- [Chi-sha] Mr. Liu.
- [gasps]

242
00:14:33,375 --> 00:14:35,416
[tense music playing]

243
00:14:39,875 --> 00:14:42,041
Uh… the money's all here.

244
00:14:42,125 --> 00:14:44,666
I'd do this even if you didn't pay me.

245
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:50,291
Heilung Hall members are perfect prey
for testing my malicious spirits. [laughs]

246
00:14:53,333 --> 00:14:56,041
And they died so tragically.

247
00:14:56,125 --> 00:14:58,333
- [chuckles]
- [Liu] The money's all there.

248
00:14:58,416 --> 00:15:00,916
From now on, we have no more business.

249
00:15:01,916 --> 00:15:04,916
So now you want to dispense
with me, do you?

250
00:15:05,416 --> 00:15:07,708
But when you guys approached me,

251
00:15:07,791 --> 00:15:10,166
you said you admired me.

252
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:12,416
[tense music continues]

253
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,208
- Don't contact me again.
- [man] Boss.

254
00:15:16,291 --> 00:15:19,250
- Give it, give it! Just give it to him!
- Boss! Here.

255
00:15:19,333 --> 00:15:21,333
[theme music playing]

256
00:15:30,625 --> 00:15:31,708
[chuckles menacingly]

257
00:15:31,791 --> 00:15:33,791
[techno music playing]

258
00:15:35,458 --> 00:15:38,375
[people cheering]

259
00:16:09,250 --> 00:16:11,375
[techno music continues in the background]

260
00:16:12,416 --> 00:16:13,583
You came.

261
00:16:14,583 --> 00:16:16,291
So, it's settled then.

262
00:16:16,375 --> 00:16:18,625
I'm old. My skills are fading.

263
00:16:18,708 --> 00:16:20,708
[chuckling]

264
00:16:22,791 --> 00:16:24,291
You're too modest.

265
00:16:27,333 --> 00:16:31,875
Those who are chosen
by Vasavatti aren't ordinary people.

266
00:16:31,958 --> 00:16:33,958
[tense music playing]

267
00:16:35,333 --> 00:16:39,958
Heilung Hall is now terrified
after your little performance.

268
00:16:40,041 --> 00:16:42,166
[tutting] Hmm?

269
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:43,541
[tense music builds]

270
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:52,208
I was working with Vasavatti for revenge.

271
00:16:53,041 --> 00:16:54,625
Gangsters killed my family.

272
00:16:55,291 --> 00:16:57,291
They don't deserve to live.

273
00:16:57,375 --> 00:16:59,041
But this is different.

274
00:16:59,666 --> 00:17:04,166
You and Vasavatti are colluding
to control me, to force me to kill.

275
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:07,125
I know that I cannot be saved.

276
00:17:07,666 --> 00:17:10,041
But I've never killed anyone innocent.

277
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:16,458
As an evil person myself,
I know that evil comes in different forms.

278
00:17:17,916 --> 00:17:20,958
So you and I, we're different.

279
00:17:22,583 --> 00:17:24,583
[tense music intensifies]

280
00:17:29,041 --> 00:17:30,541
So what next?

281
00:17:30,625 --> 00:17:32,416
What else do you want me to do?

282
00:17:43,166 --> 00:17:44,250
[music fades]

283
00:17:44,333 --> 00:17:45,416
CHIANG HUA-CHIH

284
00:17:46,125 --> 00:17:48,583
Based on your daughter's horoscope,

285
00:17:48,666 --> 00:17:51,666
your illness and her condition
are intertwined.

286
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:56,291
Please. Can we change our fate?

287
00:17:57,041 --> 00:17:58,625
A person's fate is…

288
00:18:00,083 --> 00:18:01,500
set in stone.

289
00:18:07,333 --> 00:18:09,333
[low growling in the background]

290
00:18:11,333 --> 00:18:16,000
However, you may eliminate karmic aura.

291
00:18:16,083 --> 00:18:17,000
Really?

292
00:18:17,083 --> 00:18:18,291
[eerie music playing]

293
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:19,416
I'll do anything.

294
00:18:20,875 --> 00:18:23,000
[Chi-sha] <i>You're wasting your talent.</i>

295
00:18:23,083 --> 00:18:25,541
[screaming]

296
00:18:27,791 --> 00:18:31,000
Indulging in these religious scams.

297
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:35,041
If you work for me,

298
00:18:35,541 --> 00:18:37,750
I'll give you everything
you ever dreamed of.

299
00:18:37,833 --> 00:18:39,500
[suspenseful music playing]

300
00:18:39,583 --> 00:18:40,541
What should I do?

301
00:18:43,458 --> 00:18:45,791
[chanting]

302
00:18:57,208 --> 00:18:59,000
Have you brought your daughter?

303
00:19:01,083 --> 00:19:02,416
[woman] Yes, Master.

304
00:19:03,333 --> 00:19:04,208
I have.

305
00:19:05,375 --> 00:19:07,958
I didn't tell you last time, but…

306
00:19:08,875 --> 00:19:12,375
your house always had an ominous aura.

307
00:19:12,458 --> 00:19:13,666
[tense music playing]

308
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:17,500
It's likely someone's
creating negative karma.

309
00:19:20,041 --> 00:19:21,791
When was your daughter born?

310
00:19:22,791 --> 00:19:25,833
In 2009, March 17.

311
00:19:27,083 --> 00:19:28,833
LUNAR FEBRUARY 21ST, YEAR OF THE OX

312
00:19:28,916 --> 00:19:32,750
- That was the Year of the Ox.
- [tense music builds]

313
00:19:32,833 --> 00:19:37,166
I'm gathering malicious spirits
refined from vital spirits.

314
00:19:37,791 --> 00:19:39,958
Find me people with these birth details.

315
00:19:40,041 --> 00:19:41,500
LUNAR FEBRUARY 21ST, YEAR OF THE OX

316
00:19:41,583 --> 00:19:43,541
And kill them.

317
00:19:43,625 --> 00:19:44,875
[music fades]

318
00:19:44,958 --> 00:19:51,750
I see now your daughter
is responsible for this karma.

319
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:53,833
Your fates clash.

320
00:19:53,916 --> 00:19:56,000
She with you, and you with her.

321
00:19:56,083 --> 00:19:59,583
This is why she's mute,
and you've been unwell.

322
00:20:00,291 --> 00:20:02,375
But it can't be due to my daughter.

323
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,833
I'm certain of her aura.

324
00:20:05,916 --> 00:20:08,208
- [tense music playing]
- Then what should I do?

325
00:20:08,291 --> 00:20:10,041
Go outside. Leave her here.

326
00:20:13,541 --> 00:20:15,750
- Go outside.
- Wait.

327
00:20:15,833 --> 00:20:18,083
- Go! Now!
- Master, wait. What are you going to do?

328
00:20:18,166 --> 00:20:19,666
- Go out.
- Yuan-yuan, come here.

329
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:22,291
- Get out! Go!
- Come here! Get off her! Yuan-yuan!

330
00:20:22,375 --> 00:20:23,375
[music stops]

331
00:20:24,208 --> 00:20:26,541
Mr. Han? Here's the lighter.

332
00:20:27,833 --> 00:20:29,083
[lighter clicking]

333
00:20:47,125 --> 00:20:49,125
[bird chirping]

334
00:20:49,208 --> 00:20:51,208
[intriguing music playing]

335
00:20:57,416 --> 00:20:59,875
SHEN-LUNG CROWN PRINCE HARMS PEOPLE

336
00:21:01,083 --> 00:21:03,791
- There it is again.
- What?

337
00:21:03,875 --> 00:21:05,875
[music builds]

338
00:21:11,166 --> 00:21:14,291
Shen-Lung Crown Prince has appeared
three times this month.

339
00:21:14,375 --> 00:21:16,000
This one warned about scams,

340
00:21:16,083 --> 00:21:18,083
and the second one
about him being bewitched.

341
00:21:19,208 --> 00:21:22,375
You didn't pay much attention to this,
and now things are worse.

342
00:21:24,125 --> 00:21:24,958
I'm to blame?

343
00:21:25,708 --> 00:21:27,500
I have a ton of work still to do.

344
00:21:27,583 --> 00:21:29,291
There's only one of me.

345
00:21:29,375 --> 00:21:31,916
[intriguing music continues]

346
00:21:32,583 --> 00:21:35,916
There are so many religious scammers.
I can't capture them all.

347
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,083
And now there's this Demon King invasion.

348
00:21:38,166 --> 00:21:40,833
Why must I bother with that trivial stuff?

349
00:21:40,916 --> 00:21:42,125
Fuck.

350
00:21:43,583 --> 00:21:45,291
Mr. Han? Where are you going?

351
00:21:48,250 --> 00:21:49,500
[music fades]

352
00:21:49,583 --> 00:21:51,583
[knocking]

353
00:21:53,166 --> 00:21:55,166
[eerie music playing]

354
00:21:58,041 --> 00:21:59,041
Yuan?

355
00:21:59,625 --> 00:22:00,791
Mr. Han.

356
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:02,875
What's she…

357
00:22:15,333 --> 00:22:16,958
[demonic breathing]

358
00:22:19,416 --> 00:22:21,416
[eerie music continues]

359
00:22:27,041 --> 00:22:28,208
Who was it?

360
00:22:28,291 --> 00:22:29,875
Who did this to you?

361
00:22:29,958 --> 00:22:30,833
Where's your mom?

362
00:22:39,833 --> 00:22:41,958
I'm going down to hell. Help me.

363
00:22:42,041 --> 00:22:42,875
How?

364
00:22:45,041 --> 00:22:46,958
[dramatic music playing]

365
00:22:47,708 --> 00:22:49,166
I've done this before.

366
00:22:49,875 --> 00:22:52,833
I used the pogs
to make myself unconscious.

367
00:22:54,791 --> 00:22:56,000
[music builds]

368
00:22:56,583 --> 00:22:59,708
Three minutes after I pass out, play this.

369
00:23:01,583 --> 00:23:03,250
Then shock me with this.

370
00:23:06,625 --> 00:23:08,291
[exhaling]

371
00:23:12,041 --> 00:23:13,291
I'm counting on you.

372
00:23:15,458 --> 00:23:17,875
[dramatic music intensifies]

373
00:23:22,833 --> 00:23:24,041
[muffled groaning]

374
00:23:38,791 --> 00:23:40,416
[watch ticking]

375
00:23:42,833 --> 00:23:44,833
- [gasps]
- [music subsides]

376
00:23:47,833 --> 00:23:48,666
[exclaims]

377
00:23:57,083 --> 00:24:00,333
WEST

378
00:24:00,416 --> 00:24:02,416
[eerie music playing]

379
00:24:22,333 --> 00:24:24,333
[sobbing]

380
00:24:25,333 --> 00:24:26,500
[Han Chieh] Ms. Chiang.

381
00:24:31,166 --> 00:24:32,166
What happened?

382
00:24:33,083 --> 00:24:34,250
I can't find her.

383
00:24:34,333 --> 00:24:38,041
I can't find my daughter anywhere.
She died before me.

384
00:24:39,083 --> 00:24:40,375
I can't find her.

385
00:24:40,458 --> 00:24:41,666
Where's her spirit?

386
00:24:42,166 --> 00:24:44,208
[eerie music continues]

387
00:24:44,291 --> 00:24:45,458
I don't know.

388
00:24:45,541 --> 00:24:48,625
She can't be here without her spirit.

389
00:24:49,250 --> 00:24:50,083
Who did this?

390
00:24:53,875 --> 00:24:55,125
Shen-Lung.

391
00:24:55,208 --> 00:24:58,166
Open the door! Yuan-yuan! Yuan-yuan!

392
00:24:58,666 --> 00:25:01,166
Open the door! Please, Master.

393
00:25:01,875 --> 00:25:02,958
Yuan-yuan!

394
00:25:03,041 --> 00:25:04,250
[yelps]

395
00:25:06,708 --> 00:25:08,708
[suspenseful music playing]

396
00:25:13,916 --> 00:25:15,708
- [gasps]
- [Yuan-yuan groaning]

397
00:25:28,250 --> 00:25:29,625
[screams]

398
00:25:46,583 --> 00:25:48,583
[suspenseful music continues]

399
00:25:52,125 --> 00:25:54,250
I got my daughter killed.

400
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,458
I got myself killed.

401
00:25:59,708 --> 00:26:02,000
- Where is he?
- He's in the temple.

402
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:04,958
[mysterious music playing]

403
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:18,791
["The Maiden's Prayer"
playing over headphones]

404
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,166
WEST

405
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:24,625
[Han Chieh] Time's up.

406
00:26:25,916 --> 00:26:28,583
- Where are you going?
- To deal with that garbage.

407
00:26:29,083 --> 00:26:30,791
[clock ticking]

408
00:26:35,833 --> 00:26:38,083
[Chiang Hua-Chih] How? What will you do?

409
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:42,541
- Are you still alive?
- Strictly speaking, I'm dead.

410
00:26:42,625 --> 00:26:44,250
[mysterious music continues]

411
00:26:50,666 --> 00:26:52,083
Who exactly really?

412
00:26:52,666 --> 00:26:55,208
I serve the Third Crown Prince.

413
00:26:57,833 --> 00:27:00,833
- [coughing]
- [music fades]

414
00:27:02,958 --> 00:27:04,791
Why did you shock me so hard?

415
00:27:05,583 --> 00:27:08,250
You didn't tell me
how high the setting should be.

416
00:27:08,916 --> 00:27:10,583
[groans] My clothes.

417
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:13,500
[coughing]

418
00:27:15,166 --> 00:27:17,708
And the lotus.
There's lotus in the fridge.

419
00:27:32,875 --> 00:27:35,625
Tell Chang Min there'll be a murder
in Shen-Lung Temple.

420
00:27:35,708 --> 00:27:36,583
And you?

421
00:27:37,875 --> 00:27:39,708
I'm settling a score.

422
00:27:40,541 --> 00:27:42,333
[theme music playing]

423
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:45,750
QIANKUN HOOP

424
00:27:59,125 --> 00:28:01,208
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

425
00:28:11,125 --> 00:28:13,125
[theme music continues]

426
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:19,875
Go!

427
00:28:19,958 --> 00:28:22,083
[women clamoring]

428
00:28:22,166 --> 00:28:26,458
The Third Crown Prince's agent.
I'm humbled.

429
00:28:26,541 --> 00:28:28,250
I'll give you a chance.

430
00:28:28,333 --> 00:28:30,375
Give me the girl's spirit,
and I'll spare you.

431
00:28:30,458 --> 00:28:33,500
[laughs] The Third Crown Prince is a brat.

432
00:28:33,583 --> 00:28:36,208
I see that's passed on to you.

433
00:28:36,708 --> 00:28:39,541
Okay. I won't only beat you to a pulp,

434
00:28:39,625 --> 00:28:41,541
you'll lose bladder control.

435
00:28:42,041 --> 00:28:44,041
[tense music playing]

436
00:28:53,125 --> 00:28:56,041
[music becomes eerie]

437
00:28:57,250 --> 00:28:58,166
[grunts]

438
00:29:27,125 --> 00:29:28,583
[action music playing]

439
00:29:28,666 --> 00:29:30,375
Third Crown Prince, huh?

440
00:29:30,458 --> 00:29:31,791
- This is all he's got?
- [groans]

441
00:29:48,583 --> 00:29:51,291
Tell the old fool
to come collect your corpse.

442
00:29:52,125 --> 00:29:54,416
[music distorts]

443
00:29:59,833 --> 00:30:01,833
[theme music playing]

444
00:30:18,458 --> 00:30:21,583
[the Crown Prince] You're very arrogant,
aren't you? Shouting at me like that.

445
00:30:22,250 --> 00:30:25,500
You can't beat a scammer?
Even a simple task like that--

446
00:30:25,583 --> 00:30:26,708
You think I want this?

447
00:30:27,375 --> 00:30:28,250
[coughs]

448
00:30:28,333 --> 00:30:31,166
- Where are the pogs I gave you?
- I've used them all.

449
00:30:32,375 --> 00:30:33,375
Didn't you see?

450
00:30:36,916 --> 00:30:38,291
[action music continues]

451
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,750
The pogs you gave me,
they're like toys to him.

452
00:30:41,833 --> 00:30:44,166
[Crown Prince] You're always
complaining, aren't you?

453
00:30:44,250 --> 00:30:45,916
I don't smoke, I don't drink.

454
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:48,666
It's dirty work.
Can't I have any fun at all?

455
00:30:52,458 --> 00:30:55,250
I told you, you mustn't smoke or drink.

456
00:30:55,333 --> 00:30:58,250
Yet you used the loop
to light your cigarette.

457
00:30:58,333 --> 00:30:59,916
Have you forgotten?

458
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:04,583
The tools I give you
cause you pain after their use.

459
00:31:05,208 --> 00:31:06,875
[sighs] Do I look scared?

460
00:31:06,958 --> 00:31:09,000
[low action music continues]

461
00:31:12,625 --> 00:31:13,666
[blows]

462
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:15,208
I'll give you one more.

463
00:31:22,541 --> 00:31:24,416
[grunting]

464
00:31:24,500 --> 00:31:26,291
I told you, it's useless on him.

465
00:31:26,791 --> 00:31:28,708
<i>I've especially blessed this one.</i>

466
00:31:28,791 --> 00:31:30,583
[music stops abruptly]

467
00:31:30,666 --> 00:31:32,166
Are you quite finished?

468
00:31:32,250 --> 00:31:33,208
[sputters]

469
00:31:34,041 --> 00:31:35,333
My turn now.

470
00:31:35,416 --> 00:31:38,500
["Royal Progress of the Gods"
by JhenYueTang playing]

471
00:31:38,583 --> 00:31:39,583
[groaning]

472
00:32:15,833 --> 00:32:18,291
["Royal Progress of the Gods" continues]

473
00:32:30,458 --> 00:32:31,791
[groans]

474
00:32:34,041 --> 00:32:35,041
[grunts]

475
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:44,708
[song ends]

476
00:32:46,875 --> 00:32:49,083
[breathing heavily]

477
00:32:53,833 --> 00:32:55,833
[poignant music playing]

478
00:33:01,583 --> 00:33:02,500
[siren wailing]

479
00:33:19,916 --> 00:33:21,708
We've been looking for the scammer,

480
00:33:21,791 --> 00:33:23,916
but never been able
to pin anything on him.

481
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:26,416
This is the end of his reign of terror.

482
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:29,125
Lucky the Crown Prince
alerted you when he did.

483
00:33:30,666 --> 00:33:32,208
I should have noticed.

484
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:36,750
[poignant music continues]

485
00:33:37,291 --> 00:33:39,666
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

486
00:33:56,166 --> 00:33:58,000
DONGFENG MARKET

487
00:34:09,083 --> 00:34:10,875
[music fades]

488
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:20,916
[groans softly]

489
00:34:26,958 --> 00:34:28,958
[poignant music playing]

490
00:34:45,250 --> 00:34:48,625
Okay. Go find your mom.

491
00:35:04,833 --> 00:35:05,833
[groans softly]

492
00:35:18,416 --> 00:35:21,625
QIAN, XUN, KAN

493
00:35:21,708 --> 00:35:23,708
[eerie music playing]

494
00:35:26,750 --> 00:35:28,750
[low chants]

495
00:35:29,541 --> 00:35:31,541
[music intensifies]

496
00:35:36,416 --> 00:35:38,458
DAD: EXAM OVER YET?
ARE YOU COMING HOME NOW?

497
00:35:38,541 --> 00:35:41,166
I'M ALMOST HOME

498
00:35:50,708 --> 00:35:52,291
[music fades]

499
00:35:53,791 --> 00:35:55,291
[eerie music continues]

500
00:35:55,375 --> 00:35:57,375
[screaming]

501
00:36:03,291 --> 00:36:05,291
[music fades]

502
00:36:06,208 --> 00:36:08,208
[theme music playing]

503
00:36:52,666 --> 00:36:54,666
[music continues]

504
00:37:43,833 --> 00:37:45,833
[music continues]

505
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:30,500
[music continues]

506
00:39:24,583 --> 00:39:26,583
[music continues]

507
00:41:01,416 --> 00:41:03,708
[music ends]
